{"tid":1733156,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"蒙面法違憲！","createTime":"2019-11-18T04:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T04:56:40.000Z","uid":207763,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6d4eb923a00137c653b573c8bc7b3074eac476d0","tid":1733156,"uid":207763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:52:27.000Z","msg":"政府回歸後首次動用緊急法，以此訂立蒙面法，旋即引來多宗司法覆核挑戰，指緊急法違反人權法，高等法院早前處理由泛民提出的兩宗訴訟，今頒下判詞，裁定緊急法於「危害公安」這部份違憲、蒙面法違憲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191118&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60280089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191118%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60280089&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2TeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=3b2f6df6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191118%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60280089&h=c043e934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191118&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60280089</a>"},{"pid":"cb80b54160b11ce4fc9142a5c6fe782c9884ac00","tid":1733156,"uid":207763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:53:05.000Z","msg":"打得甩！"},{"pid":"85d056054b28691faa2fc7086177f1a16b3c726f","tid":1733156,"uid":207763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:53:34.000Z","msg":"申請一方陳詞指，蒙面法不合理地限制和平表達意見的自由，連萬聖節化妝都有被捕風險。有記者工作時被扯下防護面罩，故警方稱會用專業執法的說法，未能令人信服。此外，蒙面可以有正當理由，例如示威者跟警方一樣有人身安全憂慮，擔心被起底，以及遭僱主秋後算賬。<br />\n<br />\n政府一方則指，憑常識便知蒙面有壯膽效果，每當蒙面示威者大肆破壞但逍遙法外，法治都會受損。蒙面法即使不能阻嚇所有暴力罪犯，只要能阻嚇部份年輕人，令他們不要上街犯法，避免被捕入獄，已足以改變他們一生。政府一方更指，年輕人易受他人影響，「只要救回一個，都不會嫌少」。"},{"pid":"3cf831bc68dd4258f2da3181d0b37361af86e79b","tid":1733156,"uid":332709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:53:36.000Z","msg":"佢都會charge 暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2510775201c31d1bd9c68e30f5756d28aeda41a8","tid":1733156,"uid":159569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:53:56.000Z","msg":"總算有個好消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8425755d54e8e20e0f0d46b5e71942fbe2de7d1e","tid":1733156,"uid":207763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3cf831bc68dd4258f2da3181d0b37361af86e79b","tid":1733156,"uid":332709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:53:36.000Z","msg":"佢都會charge 暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:54:28.000Z","msg":"和理非戴返個罩都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78133fd58145813c2365f19dd79234a157f6405a","tid":1733156,"uid":207763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"反反蒙面法"},{"pid":"a722be7aa72ab700cb9c0e9b60fbf7333e955f32","tid":1733156,"uid":207763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:55:36.000Z","msg":"蒙面無罪"},{"pid":"96e6432f97c44f6e7e9d518c4fee92798b8a3bde","tid":1733156,"uid":207763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"戴罩有理"},{"pid":"f142c571f9e2066a00f15b50d4c8b20a16a9c740","tid":1733156,"uid":207717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:56:40.000Z","msg":"佢一定上訴"}]}